Title: InnerTube Download, convert, and sync YouTube videos
Description: InnerTube is a WPF application that downloads videos from YouTube, converts them to MP4 or WMV format and syncs them to iTunes or Zune.

Project Description
InnerTube is a WPF application that downloads videos from YouTube, converts them to MP4 or WMV format and syncs them to iTunes or Zune.

More details on InnerTube, including screenshots is coming soon

  • InnerTube is an application for the soon-to-be-released Coding4Fun book
  • InnerTube is available in VB and C#
  • Do not tease and taunt InnerTube
